{"id": "1296359085414809620", "channel_id": "1296359085414809620", "type": 0, "author_id": "776811138984706089", "author_name": "wild_pansy", "author_bot": false, "content": "總覺得這顆蛹比王還難打啊每三回合加固一次\n融災刷超限夠難了蘿坦刷超限傷害還越來越低\n雖然拿四小強打屬於是我的問題就是了\n所以可以幫蘿坦加個天賦了嗎owo?", "timestamp": "2024-10-17T06:28:11.150000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1296359085653889096", "filename": "Screenshot_20241017-141747343.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 121350, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1296359085414809620/1296359085653889096/Screenshot_20241017-141747343.jpg?ex=69cc123b&is=69cac0bb&hm=c200281e901c79cd620b3a248c68ef61edcdedbe1d64b356cc83e69788f45086&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1296359085414809620", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "來自四小強小小的抱怨", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
